Viacoin bech32 HRP added to Satoshi labs. In the future, most Viacoin addresses will start with `via` instead of `v` bech32 (native Segwit addr) produces smaller transactions than P2SH segwit. stronger checksumming/error detection No case sensitivity. https://github.com/satoshilabs/slips/commit/8e1855025baedb2c1bca6dd895f0791fed0ebdb1 …
